quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  74,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  74,1,ae ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) jo kapra lapete parre ho
  74,2,utho aur hadaayat karo
  74,3,aur apne perwar-digaar ki barayi karo
  74,4,aur apne kapron ko pak rakho
  74,5,aur napaaki se daur raho
  74,6,aur ( is niyat se ) ahsaan nah karo ke is se ziyada ke taalib ho
  74,7,aur apne perwar-digaar ke liye sabr karo
  74,8,jab sor phonka jaye ga
  74,9,woh din ka mushkil din hoga
  74,10,( yani ) kafiroon par aasaan nah hoga
  74,11,hamein is shakhs se samajh lainay do jis ko hum ne akela pedakiya
  74,12,aur maal kaseer diya
  74,13,aur ( har waqt is ke paas ) haazir rehne walay betay diye
  74,14,aur har terhan ke samaan mein wusat di
  74,15,abhi khwahish rakhta hai ke aur ziyada den
  74,16,aisa hargiz nahi hoga. yeh hamari ayatain ka dushman raha hai
  74,17,hum usay Saood par charhayen ge
  74,18,is ne fikarkiya aur tajweez ki
  74,19,yeh mara jaye is ne kaisi tajweez ki
  74,20,phir yeh mara jaye is ne kaisi tajweez ki
  74,21,phir tamilkiya
  74,22,phir teori charhai aur munh bigaar liya
  74,23,phir pusht phair kar chala aur ( qubool haq se ) ghuroorkiya
  74,24,phir kehnay laga ke yeh to jaadoo hai jo ( uglo se ) munhtaqil hota aaya hai
  74,25,( phir bola ) yeh ( khuda ka kalaam nahi balkay ) bashar ka kalaam hai
  74,26,hum anqareeb is ko saqar mein daakhil karen ge
  74,27,aur tumkiya samjhay ke saqarkiya hai ?
  74,28,( woh aag hai ke ) nah baqi rakhay gi aur nah chhorey gi
  74,29,aur badan jhulas kar siyah kardey gi
  74,30,is par unees Darogha hain
  74,31,aur hum ne dozakh ke Darogha farishtay banaye hain. aur un ka shumaar kafiroon ki azmaish ke liye muqarrarkiya hai ( aur ) is liye ke ahal kitaab yaqeen karen aur mominon ka imaan aur ziyada ho aur ahal kitaab aur momin shak nah layein. aur is liye ke jin logon ke dilon mein ( nifaq ka ) marz hai aur ( jo ) kafir ( hain ) kahin ke is misaal ( ke bayan karne ) se khuda ka maqsadkiya hai? isi terhan khuda jis ko chahta hai gumraah karta hai aur jis ko chahta hai hadaayat karta hai aur tumahray perwar-digaar ke lashkaron ko is ke siwa koi nahi jaanta. aur yeh to bani aadam ke liye nasiyaat hai
  74,32,haan haan ( hamein ) chaand ki qasam
  74,33,aur raat ki jab peeth phairnay lagey
  74,34,aur subah ki jab roshan ho
  74,35,ke woh ( aag ) aik bohat barri ( aafat ) hai
  74,36,( aur ) bani aadam ke liye moajib khauf
  74,37,jo tum mein se agay barhna chahay ya peechay rehna chahay
  74,38,har shakhs apne aamaal ke badlay guru hai
  74,39,magar dahni taraf walay ( naik log )
  74,40,( ke ) woh baghaye bahisht mein ( hon ge aur ) puchhte hon ge
  74,41,( yani aag mein julne walay ) gunahgaaron se
  74,42,ke tum dozakh mein kyun parre ?
  74,43,woh jawab den ge ke hum namaz nahi parhte they
  74,44,aur nah faqeero ko khana khelati they
  74,45,aur ahal baatil ke sath mil kar ( haq se ) inkaar karte they
  74,46,aur roz jaza ko jutlatay they
  74,47,yahan taq ke hamein mout aagai
  74,48,( to is haal mein ) sifarish karne walon ki sifarish un ke haq mein kuch faida nah day gi
  74,49,un kokiya howa hai ke nasiyaat se rugardan ho rahay hain
  74,50,goya gadhay hain ke bidak jatay hain
  74,51,( yani ) sher se dar kar bhaag jatay hain
  74,52,asal yeh hai ke un mein se har shakhs yeh chahta hai ke is ke paas khuli hui kitaab aeye
  74,53,aisa hargiz nahi hoga. haqeeqat yeh hai ke un ko akhirat ka khauf hi nahi
  74,54,kuch shak nahi ke yeh nasiyaat hai
  74,55,to jo chahay usay yaad rakhay
  74,56,aur yaad bhi tab hi rakhen ge jab khuda chahay. wohi darny ke Laiq aur bakhshish ka maalik hai
